      "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nAlex, I am not sure whether it is suitable to move ot_declare_* into osd_thread_info or not. Because the ot_declare_xxx are unnecessary for non-mofication operations, such as stat/lookup. Since the ot_declare_xxx can be allocated together with the transaction handle, keeping them there may not cause much overhead.",
